Calculate ka matrix for Goodman and Stern (1962) model

calculate_ka_matrix.Rd

Calculate ka matrix for Goodman and Stern (1962) model

Usage

calculate_ka_matrix(
  frequency,
  sound_speed_sw,
  sound_speed_fluid,
  sound_speed_longitudinal,
  sound_speed_transversal,
  radius_shell,
  radius_fluid
)

Arguments

frequency

Frequency vector

sound_speed_sw

Seawater sound speed

sound_speed_fluid

Fluid sound speed

sound_speed_longitudinal

Longitudinal sound speed in shell

sound_speed_transversal

Transversal sound speed in shell

radius_shell

Shell radius

radius_fluid

Fluid radius

Value

Matrix of ka values
